00:00:34.112 --> 00:00:37.293
We're going to continue our study on the

00:00:37.433 --> 00:00:38.534
last word picture.

00:00:38.554 --> 00:00:41.335
This is a derivative of a program we

00:00:41.375 --> 00:00:44.417
began a month ago seeking to understand

00:00:45.490 --> 00:00:47.792
the whole intervention that took place

00:00:48.012 --> 00:00:51.533
with Dowd as a result of him being

00:00:51.594 --> 00:00:54.636
visited by a surrogate mother of whom he

00:00:54.695 --> 00:00:56.698
had some extraordinary things to say and

00:00:56.978 --> 00:00:59.018
who said some extraordinary things to him

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:01.881
uh it was uh one of the real

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:03.923
eye openers uh i've been

00:01:04.746 --> 00:01:08.308
working alongside Yahowah now for twenty-five

00:01:08.349 --> 00:01:10.450
years, have written thirty-five books,

00:01:10.469 --> 00:01:12.070
twenty-five thousand pages,

00:01:12.111 --> 00:01:15.412
have a hundred thousand hours invested in

00:01:15.572 --> 00:01:19.115
this enterprise, and have done many,

00:01:19.316 --> 00:01:22.477
many thousands upon thousands of radio

00:01:22.518 --> 00:01:25.418
interviews and now a thousand hours of the

00:01:25.558 --> 00:01:26.200
Yahowah blog.

00:01:26.219 --> 00:01:29.221
And in all of that time,

00:01:30.281 --> 00:01:32.483
there are a handful of things that we

00:01:32.522 --> 00:01:33.144
come across.

00:01:34.069 --> 00:01:37.753
that just profoundly changed the way we

00:01:38.173 --> 00:01:38.873
look at things,

00:01:38.933 --> 00:01:42.075
that caused us to grow exponentially.

00:01:42.897 --> 00:01:44.918
That last word picture,

00:01:44.977 --> 00:01:49.600
the thirty-first Mashal, was one of them.

00:01:51.783 --> 00:01:54.745
We recognize that based upon it,

00:01:55.486 --> 00:01:57.888
based upon what was written,

00:01:58.427 --> 00:02:02.230
that Dowd said and did in Second Samuel,

00:02:03.334 --> 00:02:04.754
and how horrific that was.

00:02:04.875 --> 00:02:07.837
And then Dowd's response to God,

00:02:07.917 --> 00:02:10.277
blaming God for the predicament that he

00:02:10.338 --> 00:02:13.180
made in the fifty first Psalm.

00:02:15.762 --> 00:02:18.883
That literally the fate of humanity hung

00:02:18.924 --> 00:02:22.406
in the balance if Dowd couldn't get his

00:02:22.485 --> 00:02:24.548
act together and he had really spiraled

00:02:24.608 --> 00:02:26.549
out of control and there was no one

00:02:26.588 --> 00:02:27.990
that seemed to be able to get his

00:02:28.030 --> 00:02:28.629
attention,

00:02:29.069 --> 00:02:29.270
not

00:02:30.979 --> 00:02:32.620
Not Joab, not Nathan,

00:02:33.600 --> 00:02:34.701
and no one else around him,

00:02:34.762 --> 00:02:36.323
certainly not any of his wives,

00:02:36.362 --> 00:02:37.963
not any of his advisors,

00:02:38.443 --> 00:02:39.625
not a prophet during the day.

00:02:39.705 --> 00:02:41.445
No one got his attention.

00:02:42.247 --> 00:02:43.347
He was in a spiral,

00:02:43.867 --> 00:02:47.330
and it was spinning out of control very

00:02:47.370 --> 00:02:48.270
quickly.

00:02:48.950 --> 00:02:50.893
And so we realized that the...

00:02:52.260 --> 00:02:53.861
Thirty-first Mashal

00:02:54.502 --> 00:02:56.824
was an intervention to sober him up,

00:02:57.224 --> 00:03:00.288
to get him thinking appropriately,

00:03:00.647 --> 00:03:01.990
get him to understand who he was.

00:03:03.151 --> 00:03:04.532
But it wasn't nearly enough.

00:03:05.853 --> 00:03:07.895
And what followed was the Eighty-Ninth

00:03:08.014 --> 00:03:08.455
Mizmowr,

00:03:08.556 --> 00:03:12.979
where Ethan ha Ezrachy the perpetually

00:03:13.759 --> 00:03:14.580
deployed one.

00:03:16.573 --> 00:03:18.334
co-authored this with Yahowah.

00:03:19.414 --> 00:03:22.956
And it was designed to lay it all

00:03:23.037 --> 00:03:23.537
on the line,

00:03:23.817 --> 00:03:26.359
to explain to Dowd exactly who he was,

00:03:26.378 --> 00:03:27.579
what was expected of him,

00:03:28.020 --> 00:03:29.920
what was required to finish the job,

00:03:30.681 --> 00:03:33.163
how he was going to redeem himself and

00:03:33.203 --> 00:03:33.742
his people,

00:03:33.902 --> 00:03:36.865
how he was going to enable the benefits

00:03:36.944 --> 00:03:41.167
of the covenant again to resolve his

00:03:41.227 --> 00:03:44.429
crisis as well as the ongoing crisis of

00:03:44.449 --> 00:03:44.868
his people.

00:03:45.753 --> 00:03:46.914
And all the while,

00:03:46.935 --> 00:03:48.496
what we learned is that Dowd,

00:03:49.276 --> 00:03:53.938
without a decent mother and father in this

00:03:54.019 --> 00:03:54.998
particular life,

00:03:55.759 --> 00:03:58.441
came to represent Yisrael.

00:03:58.661 --> 00:04:00.442
He was as belligerent as his people,

00:04:00.481 --> 00:04:03.723
as misguided as the rest of Yahuwdym.

00:04:04.104 --> 00:04:07.586
He was an example and to a large

00:04:07.605 --> 00:04:08.947
degree of what not to do.

00:04:11.584 --> 00:04:12.804
That had to change,

00:04:12.843 --> 00:04:16.045
but the purpose of him coming across like

00:04:16.084 --> 00:04:20.966
the rest of Israel was to show that

00:04:21.665 --> 00:04:23.846
that could be resolved and that what Dowd

00:04:23.867 --> 00:04:24.947
would do would resolve it.

00:04:25.627 --> 00:04:27.348
But it would only resolve it when his

00:04:27.408 --> 00:04:30.889
relationship with Yahowah was resolved.

00:04:31.588 --> 00:04:32.069
And for that,

00:04:32.108 --> 00:04:33.408
there would be an intervention.

00:04:34.288 --> 00:04:39.790
It's a profound perspective of how Yahowah

00:04:39.831 --> 00:04:40.430
goes about

00:04:41.946 --> 00:04:43.706
solving serious problems.

00:04:44.107 --> 00:04:45.668
And you look back at time and there's

00:04:45.687 --> 00:04:48.369
a number of places where God intervened a

00:04:48.449 --> 00:04:51.531
very similar way with souls that he

00:04:51.571 --> 00:04:55.172
trusted to resolve crises.

00:04:55.512 --> 00:04:57.192
And that's how he got to know who

00:04:57.233 --> 00:04:59.093
he could trust, who we could rely upon,

00:04:59.553 --> 00:05:00.915
who would get the job done,

00:05:00.975 --> 00:05:04.036
who would exemplify the very

00:05:04.115 --> 00:05:09.079
characteristics that were important to

00:05:09.139 --> 00:05:09.439
Yahowah.

00:05:10.935 --> 00:05:13.916
So continuing where we left off our last

00:05:13.956 --> 00:05:16.737
time, I would share that God said,

